I was just pointing out that the &quot;average wizard&quot; is a highly morphous entity. Sometimes he's level 60 with epic and hanging out with people who do NToV regularly. Sometimes he's level 34, learning to quad ulthorks. Sometimes he's level 51, trying to get into a group in KC instead of going to kite in CS.<br>
