FT stacking only matters to someone who can actually GET more than one FT item<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Yes for the few Wizards who can put together an aggregate FT15 that's really great. But most won't ever and those that do are in the endgame, whereas the melee boosts are much easier to come by and easily available at much lower level.<br>
<br>
Don't misunderstand me, I have no problem with items being hard to get, but anyone can see that FT is the only thing that increases DPH for a wizard. Weapons do it for melees. And the weapons are _much_ easier to upgrade than it is for casters to acquire FT items.<br>
